The global goat milk yogurt market is witnessing steady growth due to increasing consumer awareness regarding the health benefits of goat milk products. Factors such as lactose intolerance, a preference for natural and organic products, and a growing focus on healthy eating habits are driving the demand for goat milk yogurt. Flavored variants of goat milk yogurt are particularly popular among consumers looking for a tasty and nutritious snack option. In addition, the availability of goat milk yogurt through various distribution channels like supermarkets, convenience stores, and online retail platforms is further fueling market growth.

